==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: făn chún xiāng jī
===Idiom===
'''[[反]][[脣]][[相]][[稽]]'''
# to make a sarcastic remark rather than submit another's criticism; to rebut with sarcastic remarks; to make a sarcastic comeback; to talk back

===Alternate forms===
*[[反唇相讥]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
*[[反唇相譏]]
*[[反脣相稽]], [[反唇相稽]]

